						<h3 class="md:ml-auto md:text-xl max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-75">Design and technology make a great pairing—luckily, I have a background in both. Currently, I'm a VP of Product Design working for a startup based out of Brooklyn.</h3>
						<ul class="md:hidden flex flex-row mt-12">
							<li class="mr-3">
								<a class="flex items-center" href="https://dribbble.com/adamrobertson" target="_blank">
									<Image class="w-8 mr-0.5" src={dribbble} alt="Dribbble icon."/>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li class="mx-3">
								<a class="flex items-center" href="https://github.com/admrbsn" target="_blank">
									<Image class="w-8 mr-0.5" src={github} alt="Github icon."/>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li class="mx-3">
								<a class="flex items-center" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/admrbsn/" target="_blank">
									<Image class="w-8 mr-0.5" src={linkedin} alt="LinkedIn icon."/>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li class="mx-3">
								<a class="flex items-center" href="mailto:hi@adam.build">
