								</a>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<Image class="w-[91.45px] md:w-1/3 md:ml-12 mb-6 md:mb-0 rounded-sm md:rounded-xl shadow-[12px_12px_36px_-0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]" src={adam} alt="Portrait of Adam Robertson."/>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- About section -->
			<div id="about" class="md:max-w-5xl md:flex-row md:my-24 md:mx-auto md:px-0 md:pb-0 relative z-40 flex flex-col px-3 pb-12 mt-12 bg-white">
				<div class="md:order-none md:max-w-2xl md:mr-auto order-1">
					<p class="mb-8 text-base leading-relaxed opacity-75">I am always seeking to grow my <a class="highlight has-tooltip relative" href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/lisabodell/2020/08/28/futurethink-forecasts-t-shaped-teams-are-the-future-of-work/" target="_blank"><span class="tooltip left-1/2 whitespace-nowrap absolute px-2 py-1 -mt-6 text-xs text-white -translate-x-1/2 bg-black rounded shadow-lg">Forbes article on T-Shape in work</span>T-shape</a>, whether it's through reading usability studies, experimenting with new tools, or exploring different JavaScript libraries. My expertise lies in UX design and frontend development. I believe that good design is what sets the best products apart from the rest. One of my favorite quotes is by Charles Eames, "The details are not the details - They make the design." I am always attentive to the details in typography, alignment, colors and clean code.</p>
					<p class="mb-8 text-base leading-relaxed opacity-75">I am originally from northwestern Ohio and moved to Colorado after completing my Bachelor's degree in Foreign Affairs. I have been building websites <a class="highlight has-tooltip relative" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20020930020107/https://sccresources.com/" target="_blank"><span class="tooltip left-1/2 whitespace-nowrap absolute px-2 py-1 -mt-6 text-xs text-white -translate-x-1/2 bg-black rounded shadow-lg">My first commercial website from 2002</span>since the age of 16</a> and have worked in some capacity for various businesses and startups. In my free time, I enjoy hiking, cooking, DIY projects and spending time with my family.</p>
					<p class="mb-4 font-bold">I consider myself an expert in the following:</p>
					<div id="skills" class="columns-2">
						<ul>
							<li class="flex items-center py-1.5 font-semibold"><div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 mr-2 border-2 border-black rounded-sm"><Image class="absolute w-full h-full" src={webflowLogoOutline} alt="Webflow logo."/><Image aria-hidden="true" class="absolute w-full h-full" src={webflowLogo} alt="Webflow logo."/></div>Webflow</li>
							<li class="flex items-center py-1.5 font-semibold"><div class="first-letter:flex relative items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 mr-2 border-2 border-black rounded-sm"><Image class="absolute w-full h-full" src={figmaLogoOutline} alt="Figma logo."/><Image aria-hidden="true" class="absolute w-full h-full" src={figmaLogo} alt="Figma logo."/></div>Figma</li>
							<li class="flex items-center py-1.5 font-semibold"><div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 mr-2 border-2 border-black rounded-sm"><Image class="absolute w-full h-full" src={tailwindLogoOutline} alt="Tailwind logo."/><Image aria-hidden="true" class="absolute w-full h-full" src={tailwindLogo} alt="Tailwind logo."/></div>Tailwind</li>
